    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014honestly, it still runs like a dream! It\u2019s perfect for anyone looking for a dependable, stylish ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy. Drop me a message if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. To ensure long-term mechanical integrity, this vehicle has undergone a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for this chassis. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, maintaining the precise turn-in and neutral handling characteristics provided by its 50/50 weight distribution. Power is managed via the factory Variable M Differential Lock, providing excellent traction through high-lateral-G cornering. A mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
